<p>When I set value for EditText all work good, but when I press in "Enter" button I get Shutting Down VM.</p>  <p>This is fragment from xml-layout:</p>  <pre><code>&lt;com...view.widget.material.MaterialEditText         android:id="@+id/mileage_block"         style="@style/FormsMediumNumericMaterialEditText"         android:layout_height="wrap_content"         android:gravity="top"         android:textSize="@dimen/mat_forms_medium_edit_text_size"         android:layout_marginRight="16dp"         android:layout_toRightOf="@+id/vertical_divider"         android:layout_weight="1"         android:maxLength="9"         android:hint="@string/current_mileage"         android:nextFocusDown="@null"         android:nextFocusForward="@null"         app:floatingLabelText="@string/current_mileage"         app:iconLeft="@drawable/mat_milage" /&gt; </code></pre>  <ul> <li>I use custom EditText <a href="https://github.com/rengwuxian/MaterialEditText" rel="nofollow">from here</a></li> </ul>  <p>Next EditText field:</p>  <pre><code>&lt;com...view.widget.material.MaterialEditText     android:id="@+id/fuel_type_block"     style="@style/FormsMediumMaterialEditText"     android:layout_height="wrap_content"     android:textSize="@dimen/mat_forms_medium_edit_text_size"     android:layout_toRightOf="@+id/vertical_divider"     android:layout_weight="1"     android:drawableRight="@drawable/mat_spinner_arrow_down"     android:editable="false"     android:focusable="false"     android:singleLine="true"     android:focusableInTouchMode="false"     android:hint="@string/fuel_type"     android:layout_marginTop="@dimen/mat_card_inner_padding"     android:layout_marginLeft="5dp"     android:paddingRight="@dimen/mat_padding_right_edt_arrow_down"     app:floatingLabelText="@string/fuel_type"     app:iconLeft="@drawable/dn_7_ic_fuel" /&gt; </code></pre>  <p>Also I use TextWatcher for this EditText:</p>  <pre><code>private final class EditTextWatcher implements TextWatcher {       public EditTextWatcher() {                }      @Override     public void beforeTextChanged(CharSequence charSequence, int i, int i2, int i3) {                 }      @Override     public void onTextChanged(CharSequence charSequence, int i, int i2, int i3) {                        int mileage = 0;                 try {                     mileage = Integer.parseInt(charSequence.toString());                 } catch (Exception e) {                     break;                 }                  if (mCar.getOdometerType() == Constants.ODOMETER_TYPE_KM) {                     mCar.setCarRun(mileage);                 } else {                     mileage = (int) Math.round(mileage * Constants.MILE_VS_KM);                     mCar.setCarRun(mileage);                 }          }     }      @Override     public void afterTextChanged(Editable editable) {     } } </code></pre>  <p>Add screenshot with this screen. <a href="http://i.stack.imgur.com/Es7Wh.jpg" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://i.stack.imgur.com/Es7Wh.jpg" alt="enter image description here"></a></p>